## Overview

Add subtitle capability to AudioFlam in two modes:

**Mode A — Audiogram subtitles:** burn subtitles into the existing audiogram canvas export.

**Mode B — Video subtitle page:** a new tab where users upload a device video, optionally trim it, add subtitles and a title, then export.

Both modes share a single subtitle engine. The engine must be built as a fully self-contained module with no dependencies on audiogram-specific components, so it can be extracted to a standalone app in future without rework.

